name: Take Me
description:
Creator: NARS

Nina Kraviz is an internationally renowned Siberian electronic music artist, known for her critically acclaimed discography and DJ mixes. Hailed as “DJ of the Year” by Mixmag and one of Billboard’s “25 Female DJs You Need to Know,” Nina's creative and strong personality, unique music style, and constant pursuit of deeper feeling makes her one of the most standout international music talents.
